{
  "stem": "15768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It, it was general bedlam.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were small children, crying children, infants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At any rate, as this became official, we had to pull ourselves together and started walking towards the coast of France.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And again, it was a very difficult thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This time, the men really didn't follow orders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They mixed with the women and carried children and babies and gave whatever assistance was necessary.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was hot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was dusty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were all dirt roads.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we just walked and walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Some people dropped at the roadside and just couldn't make.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The farmers, again, came out and gave us water to drink to help us along.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were now coming into the summer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it was really quite difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We, at different places, we were again sort of herded into locked facilities that had been deserted so that we would not escape.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And ultimately, we ended up somewhere locked in like that at Dunkirk when the British army embarked to leave for England.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "My father had thoughts of getting us children on one of the boats to England, but that didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They weren't taking any civilians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And-- but we heard about the evacuation and the boats that came from England and the heroic thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then we were marched on to Calais, which is also a harbor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And in Calais, we were locked into what used to be a barn-type dance hall thing, everybody together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And at one point, I lost my parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I had a great deal of difficulty finding them again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But we were in this building as Calais was burning, and of course, had the thought that this was very dry wood and would very easily catch on fire and burn as well.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But everything was locked.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
